26 SECTION 2. Arkansas Code Title 6, Chapter 17, Subchapter 1, is amended
27 to add an additional section to read as follows:
28 6-17-125. School nurses — Compensation.
29 (a) As used in this section, "school nurse" means a licensed nurse
30 engaging in school nursing activities.
31 (b) Each school district board of directors shall:
32 (1) Except as otherwise provided by this section, pay school
33 nurses a minimum base salary that is at least equal to the minimum base
34 salary required for classroom teachers by § 6-17-2403; and
35 (2) Adopt a school nurse salary schedule that incorporates the
36 same or similar factors and steps as those used to establish and incorporated
